modules.description: This module applies pixel-wise expressions to images using Lwt for asynchronous evaluation. It constructs filters from expressions that compute pixel values based on spatial coordinates and input images, and runs these filters to produce output images. Concrete use cases include asynchronous image processing tasks like brightness adjustment, thresholding, or custom kernel operations.

This module applies pixel-wise image transformations using Lwt for asynchronous execution. It constructs filters from expressions that compute pixel values based on coordinates and input images, then runs these filters to produce output images. It supports concrete tasks like brightness adjustment, thresholding, and custom kernel operations on images.
